                        <precision match="@to" notAfter="2013" notBefore="0800" srophe:computed-end="2013-01-01" srophe:computed-start="0800-01-01"/>
                    </state>
                    <note xml:lang="en" type="corrigenda">In Dolabani's translation of Barsoum's description <quote xml:lang="syr-Syrj">ܕܐܰܢܛܝܘܟܺܝܰܐ</quote>, <quote xml:lang="syr-Syrj">ܘܐܰܡܝܐܢ</quote>, and 
